{% block contentType %}
    {% block content %}

        <div id="pressPage">

            {# TIER PITCH #}
            <div id="tierPitch" class="landingTier siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding shellVerticalPadding">

                <h1>One Sentence Pitch</h1>

                <p class="fontPrimary bodyLarge borderDashed">Just another dating app — except completely different and backed by outrageous guarantees including a great date in 30 days (for free) and the end of liars, players, cheaters, bots, and all senders of dickpics.</p>

            </div>

            {# TIER NUTSHELL #}
            <div id="tierNutshell" class="landingTier">
                <div id="logo"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/tier4logo.png') }}" alt=""></div>
                <div class="siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding clearfix">
                    <h1>In a Nutshell</h1>

                    <div id="tierNutshellBody" class="fontPrimary borderDashedLight">

                        <p>Everyone wants love. Yet 100 million Americans are still looking.</p>

                        <p>Dating apps mostly suck. Only 7% of singles make a meaningful connection that way each year.</p>

                        <p>The other 93%? They have no interest in wading through the muck to find happiness. They’re holding out for something better.</p>

                        <p>Launch is for them. We let friends play along (single or not). This allows for human matchmaking, trust scores, and user accountability.</p>

                        <p>This is the future of online dating: more thoughtfulness, less awfulness, and far, far better outcomes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# TIER DOING #}
            <div id="tierDoing" class="landingTier siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding shellVerticalPadding">

                <h3>What We're Doing</h3>
                <h1>Right Now</h1>

                <div class="fontPrimary borderDashed">
                    <div id="iconKickstarter"><img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/tier7iconKickstarter.png') }}" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <p>Our product has been shaped by hundreds of stories from daters and their friends.</p>


                    <p>Now we’re taking our designs to a larger audience for their input.</p>


                    <p>We think people want something new (and actually good).</p>


                    <p>So we’re going to ask a bunch of them on Kickstarter to give us $1.</p>


                    <p>If they love it, we’ll finish the app. If they hate it, we’re moving to Canada.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# TIER MISSION #}

            <div id="tierMission" class="landingTier">
                <div id="tierMissionBackground">
                    <div class="siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding shellVerticalPadding">
                        <h1>Our Mission</h1>
                        <div class="fontPrimary borderDashedLight">
                            <p>Reimagine Dating with an App that Works for Everyone</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="borderDashedLight bottom">&nbsp;</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div id="tierMissionBody" class="siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding shellVerticalPadding fontPrimary">
                    <h3>Why do we care?</h3>

                    <div class="borderDashed">
                        <div class="spacemanBullet">
                            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/tier4spacemen1.png') }}" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p>Good relationships are the best predictor of human health and happiness (which we want for our friends).
                        </p>
                        <div class="spacemanBullet">
                            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/tier4spacemen2.png') }}" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p>Most of us struggle to create new relationships once we become adults. But there are sensible, scientific ways to make it easier.
                        </p>
                        <br><br>
                        <p><strong>We’re just connecting the dots (and throwing out the old, terrible template).</strong></p>
                    </div>
                    <br><br>
                    <h3>We have two driving values</h3>
                    <div class="borderDashed">
                        <div class="spacemanBullet">
                            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/tier4spacemen1.png') }}" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p>We think dating could do without lying, shallowness, sexism, and infidelity.</p>
                        <div class="spacemanBullet">
                            <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/tier4spacemen2.png') }}" alt="">
                        </div>
                        <p>We think companies should be really good at listening and giving back.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            {# TIER SCREENS #}
            <div id="tierScreens" class="landingTier backgroundDark">
                <div class="siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding shellVerticalPadding">

                    <h1>App Sneak Peak</h1>
                    <div class="borderDashed">

                        <div id="appPreview" class="carousel slide" data-plugin="carousel" data-colminsize="sm" data-groupmobile="1" data-interval="8000">

                            <!-- Optional: Progress Indicators -->
                            <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                                <li data-target="#appPreview" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                                <li data-target="#appPreview" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                                <li data-target="#appPreview" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                                <li data-target="#appPreview" data-slide-to="3"></li>
                                <li data-target="#appPreview" data-slide-to="4"></li>
                                <li data-target="#appPreview" data-slide-to="5"></li>
                            </ol>

                            <!-- Wrapper for Slides -->
                            <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
                                <div class="item active">
                                    <div   class="slideContainer clearfix">
                                        <div  class="appScreenshot">
                                            <img data-spy="#appPreview" data-src="lazy" src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/app/1signUp-xs.png') }}"  data-ignorevisibility="true" alt="One-click Registration">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="centerText">
                                            <h2 class="hoverElement fontPrimary">One-click registraton</h2>
                                            <p class="smallLabel fontPrimary bold">Sign up with your Facebook account. (Don’t worry, it’s 100% private.)</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="item">
                                    <div   class="slideContainer clearfix">
                                        <div  class="appScreenshot">
                                            <img data-spy="#appPreview" data-src="lazy" src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/app/2recruit-xs.png') }}"  data-ignorevisibility="true" alt="Singles Recruit a Launch Crew">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="centerText">
                                            <h2 class="hoverElement fontPrimary">Singles recruit a Launch Crew</h2>
                                            <p class="smallLabel fontPrimary bold">Singles invite two or more close friends (single or partnered) to verify their account, describe them, and increase their trust score.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="item">
                                    <div   class="slideContainer clearfix">
                                        <div  class="appScreenshot">
                                            <img data-spy="#appPreview" data-src="lazy" src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/app/3matchmakerMatches-xs.png') }}"  data-ignorevisibility="true" alt="Launch Crew Suggests Matches">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="centerText">
                                            <h2 class="hoverElement fontPrimary">Launch Crew suggests matches</h2>
                                            <p class="smallLabel fontPrimary bold">Crews use their insights to review and suggest matches for their single friends to consider.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="item">
                                    <div   class="slideContainer clearfix">
                                        <div  class="appScreenshot">
                                            <img data-spy="#appPreview" data-src="lazy" src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/app/4reviewMatch-xs.png') }}"  data-ignorevisibility="true" alt="Singles review their matches">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="centerText">
                                            <h2 class="hoverElement fontPrimary">Singles review their matches</h2>
                                            <p class="smallLabel fontPrimary bold">First, they read through an honest and non-cliche profile that gives them a lot of real insight. Then they can choose to answer a few playful ice-breakers to bring the photo into focus and unlock full chat.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="item">
                                    <div   class="slideContainer clearfix">
                                        <div  class="appScreenshot">
                                            <img data-spy="#appPreview" data-src="lazy" src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/app/5meetup-xs.png') }}"  data-ignorevisibility="true" alt="Singles review their matches">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="centerText">
                                            <h2 class="hoverElement fontPrimary">Matches schedule a low-key meetup</h2>
                                            <p class="smallLabel fontPrimary bold">Initial talk goes well? Matches have 48 hours to schedule a meetup of no more than 45 minutes. Zero expectations. Just one coffee or drink with an interesting local they know they can trust.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <div class="item">
                                    <div   class="slideContainer clearfix">
                                        <div  class="appScreenshot">
                                            <img data-spy="#appPreview" data-src="lazy" src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/app/6followup-xs.png') }}"  data-ignorevisibility="true" alt="Matches leave friendly reviews">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="centerText">
                                            <h2 class="hoverElement fontPrimary">Matches schedule a low-key meetup</h2>
                                            <p class="smallLabel fontPrimary bold">A quick follow-up survey lets matches connect as friends, pass with positive feedback, or report problems in a constructive way.</p>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                            </div>

                            <!-- Controls -->
                            <div class="carouselControls">
                                <a class="left carousel-control" href="#appPreview" role="button" data-slide="prev" data-scroll="false">
                                    <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/carouselBack.png') }}" alt="">
                                    <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                                </a>
                                <a class="right carousel-control" href="#appPreview" role="button" data-slide="next" data-scroll="false">
                                    <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/carouselForward.png') }}" alt="">
                                    <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                                </a>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            {# TIER TESTIMONIALS #}
            <div id="tierTestimonials" class="landingTier siteMaxWidth siteSidePadding shellVerticalPadding">


                <h1>Testimonials:</h1>

                <div id="tierTestimonialsBody" class="fontPrimary borderDashed">
                    <div id="quotations">
                        <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/indiegogo/quotations.png') }}" alt="">
                    </div>
                    <h4>Let’s start with how people talk about the existing options<br>(we asked a lot of people).</h4>

                    <p>Our favorite:</p>


                    <p class="bodyLarge">“This isn’t the game I want to play. But I feel like it’s the only game so I should try to make it work for me.”</p>


                    <p><em>This was from a young, attractive, whip-smart PhD student. This shouldn't be hard for her.</em></p>

                    <div class="borderDashed ornament">&nbsp;</div>
                    <p class="bodyLarge">“Dating as a millennial sometimes feels like a competition to see who can care the least.”</p>


                    <p><em>That one came from a 28 year old. Friendly, bright, beautiful — but disillusioned. And not alone in that.</em></p>

                    <div class="borderDashed ornament">&nbsp;</div>
                    <h4>When we showed people what we’ve been working on?</h4>


                    <p class="bodyLarge">“This is how real life works. Singles don't live in a bubble and OFTEN rely on close family and friends to give them input about their dating prospects. That's just part of our healthy social make-up. You've got a good thing here. I hope it catches on!!”</p>

                    <p><em>What she said.</em></p>

                    <div id="quotePeople"> <img src="{{ asset('bundles/sitetheorytemplatecustom/images/indiegogo/quotePeople.png') }}" alt="">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

